snippet.title: Iris Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Iris Gameplay Trailer 
(Remastered version with some new additional stuffs) 

This video showcases the gameplay of Iris, for those who haven't try out the game, you can check this video out. The new version will be available soon with the new additional stuffs. 

Stay updated with us at:
https://twitter.com/irisjourneygame 
http://irisjourneygame.wix.com/iris

Note: I gonna reupload a new video when the new version releases. (with the fix on the left side of earphone not being heard)
